# Pair Status Checklist — {{PLAN_ID}}

## 目的

design + test_design の pair_status を tracking する。

## drive: {{DRIVE}}

### Layer: architecture (G2 凍結)
- [ ] design artifact 起票
- [ ] test_design artifact 起票
- [ ] design 1st review (axes 5/5 passed)
- [ ] test_design 1st review (axes 5/5 passed)
- [ ] pair_status='paired' に更新
- [ ] freeze_gate='G2' で frozen

### Layer: detailed (G3 凍結)
- [ ] design artifact 起票
- [ ] test_design artifact 起票
- [ ] design 1st review (axes 5/5 passed)
- [ ] test_design 1st review (axes 5/5 passed)
- [ ] pair_status='paired' に更新
- [ ] freeze_gate='G3' で frozen

### Layer: functional (G3.functional_freeze 凍結)
- [ ] design artifact 起票
- [ ] test_design artifact 起票
- [ ] design 1st review (axes 5/5 passed)
- [ ] test_design 1st review (axes 5/5 passed)
- [ ] pair review passed
- [ ] pair_status='paired'
- [ ] freeze_gate='G3' / subgate='functional_freeze'

### sprint_type='impl' (G4 凍結、layer='functional' 必須)
- [ ] implementation artifact 起票
- [ ] baseline artifact (実テスト)
- [ ] pair_status='paired'
- [ ] freeze_gate='G4'

## 6 pair_status 遷移
- pending → design_only / test_only
- design_only / test_only → paired
- paired → failed / waived
- waived は例外のみ。理由・承認者・再起票日を記載

## 監査
- `helix gate G3 --subgate functional_freeze --plan-id {{PLAN_ID}} --drive {{DRIVE}}`
- `.helix/phase.yaml` の `sprint.current_pair_status` へ反映
